1.title: The Wizard, The Witch And the Crystal Ball

episode of.title: Dorothy and the Wizard of Oz (TV Series 2017– )

1.plot: When Queen Ozma shakes her magic snow globe, a snow cloud descends on Oz and for the first time it snows. The Ozians love the snow until it gets colder and shows no sign of letting up. Dorothy and friends must find a way to end the winter.

2.title: Tin Man and Lion in Wonderland

episode of.title: Dorothy and the Wizard of Oz (TV Series 2017– )

2.plot:
Know what this is about?
 Be the first one to add a plot.

3.title: Escape From the Crystal Ball

episode of.title: Dorothy and the Wizard of Oz (TV Series 2017– )

3.plot: The Wicked Witch recounts how she came to be trapped in the crystal ball after Dorothy melted her.

4.title: The Return of the Wicked Witch

episode of.title: Dorothy and the Wizard of Oz (TV Series 2017– )

4.plot: Dorothy poofs everyone out of the ball, but the Wicked Witch jumps into the Wizard's body and tricks Ozma into giving up her magic wand.

5.title: Three Friends and a Magic Crystal

episode of.title: Dorothy and the Wizard of Oz (TV Series 2017– )

5.plot: Dorothy and Wilhelmina get stuck together after a leaf-raking spell goes wrong, so the three friends have to find a magic crystal in the Crystal Forest that will set them free.

6.title: Toto Transformed

episode of.title: Dorothy and the Wizard of Oz (TV Series 2017– )

6.plot: Dorothy gives Toto an enchanted bell she got from Ozma, not realizing that ringing it turns him into an "Ozsquatch".

7.title: Scarecrow Knows Best

episode of.title: Dorothy and the Wizard of Oz (TV Series 2017– )

7.plot: Ozma appoints Scarecrow to build a yellow brick bridge because he's the smartest in Oz, but this makes Scarecrow afraid to admit that he has no idea how to build it.

9.title: Where-Helmina's My Broom?!

episode of.title: Dorothy and the Wizard of Oz (TV Series 2017– )

9.plot: Wilhelmina can't find her broom and thinks it was stolen, but it actually left her for Frogman because it was feeling unappreciated.

10.title: Yellow Brick Road Race

episode of.title: Dorothy and the Wizard of Oz (TV Series 2017– )

10.plot: Dorothy and the gang race the Wheelers for control of the Yellow Brick Road. Dorothy adopts a "slow and steady" strategy and wins it all.

11.title: Don't Follow the Yellow Brick Road

episode of.title: Dorothy and the Wizard of Oz (TV Series 2017– )

11.plot: Dorothy and the gang decide to explore the roads less traveled, so Nome King takes advantage of their absence by moving Emerald City underground so he can rule it.

12.title: The Tallest Munchkin

episode of.title: Dorothy and the Wizard of Oz (TV Series 2017– )

12.plot: The gang meet Devin, an abnormally tall Munchkin, and teach him to love what makes him different in time for the Munchkin Music Dance-a-thon.

13.title: Scarecrow Goes to College

episode of.title: Dorothy and the Wizard of Oz (TV Series 2017– )

13.plot: Scarecrow enrolls in Wagglebug College, so Wilhelmina casts a disguise spell so the Wicked Witch can pose as Scarecrow and try to steal the ruby slippers.

14.title: Welcome to Oz Mitch

episode of.title: Dorothy and the Wizard of Oz (TV Series 2017– )

14.plot: A storm blows Mitch, another kid from Kansas, into Oz. He's not as into it as Dorothy is, but he takes a liking to Wilhelmina, much to her annoyance.

16.title: Home Away from Home

episode of.title: Dorothy and the Wizard of Oz (TV Series 2017– )

16.plot: Dorothy is feeling homesick, so Wizard tries out his new magic on a machine to show her Kansas, but instead it zaps Kansas into Oz.

17.title: The Vault Heist

episode of.title: Dorothy and the Wizard of Oz (TV Series 2017– )

17.plot: Ozma asks Dorothy to house-sit while she's out of town, so of course the Wicked Witch takes advantage by attempting a heist into Ozma's top secret magic vault.

18.title: Witch One's the Boss?

episode of.title: Dorothy and the Wizard of Oz (TV Series 2017– )

18.plot: The gang helps the Wizard practice his new magic powers while Wilhelmina tricks the Wicked Witch into doing chores under the guise of getting her powers back.

19.title: Wingmen No More

episode of.title: Dorothy and the Wizard of Oz (TV Series 2017– )

19.plot: Wilhelmina confiscates Frank and Lyman's wings after they mess up another plot. Their wings land on Lion and Scarecrow, so the monkeys go to Dorothy to get them back.

20.title: Hammer Time

episode of.title: Dorothy and the Wizard of Oz (TV Series 2017– )

20.plot: Wilhelmina uses flying hammerhead sharks to destroy a new museum in Munchkinland that put in a "Good Witch" exhibit but not one for"Bad Witches".

21.title: Jest Kidding

episode of.title: Dorothy and the Wizard of Oz (TV Series 2017– )

21.plot: The new jester bombs his first performance with jokes that are too mean, but the Wicked Witch takes advantage of his insecurity to give him a charm that induces uncontrollable laughter during his next try- so that she can immobilize Dorothy and get the ruby slippers.

22.title: Sisterhood of the Witch

episode of.title: Dorothy and the Wizard of Oz (TV Series 2017– )

22.plot: Mean Jean the Green takes the Wicked Witch's castle after discovering WW lost her powers, forcing WW to ask Wizard for help getting it back.

23.title: The Old Classic

episode of.title: Dorothy and the Wizard of Oz (TV Series 2017– )

23.plot: Fed up with Wilhelmina's constant attempts to steal the ruby slippers, Ozma casts a spell to take away Wilhelmina's magic for three days.

24.title: Too Predictable

episode of.title: Dorothy and the Wizard of Oz (TV Series 2017– )

24.plot: The Wizard accidentally creates a machine that prints out predictions, but the Wicked Witch and Wilhelmina steal it to try and capture Dorothy and her ruby slippers.

25.title: Oztember Surprise

episode of.title: Dorothy and the Wizard of Oz (TV Series 2017– )

25.plot: The Wicked Witch poses as the Wizard's long lost niece to trick him into giving her powers for the 1st of Oztember.

26.title: Sir Hokus of Pokes

episode of.title: Dorothy and the Wizard of Oz (TV Series 2017– )

26.plot: When the legendary but down-on-his-luck Sir Hokus of Pokes rides into town, Dorothy and the gang enlist the Woozy to fake a battle to restore Sir Hokus' faith in himself.

1.title: Beware the Woozy/Magical Mandolin

episode of.title: Dorothy and the Wizard of Oz (TV Series 2017– )

1.plot: Ozma accidentally turns herself to stone and Dorothy needs hairs from the fearsome woozy's tail to make an antidote, before the Nome King takes over Oz in Ozma's absence. Wilhelmina steals the Magical Mandolin that by day makes people dance, but by night puts people in a trance.

2.title: Toto Unleashed/Official Ozian Exam

episode of.title: Dorothy and the Wizard of Oz (TV Series 2017– )

2.plot: Ozma's potion of the month club package arrives and Ozma can't wait to try it! Unfortunately, Dorothy doesn't read the instructions before she spritz Ozma with the Perfume of Petrification. A Boomerang original.

3.title: Locket Locket in My Pocket/Mixed-Up Mixer

episode of.title: Dorothy and the Wizard of Oz (TV Series 2017– )

3.plot: Wilhelmina uses a magic locket to pose as Dorothy at an Oz jamboree fair. While teaching Ozma to bake, Dorothy accidentally brings the mixer to life and causes the gang's bodies to get all mixed up with each other, Exquisite Corpse-style.

4.title: Ojo the Unlucky/The Lion's Share

episode of.title: Dorothy and the Wizard of Oz (TV Series 2017– )

4.plot: Dorothy and the gang need to take Ojo the Unlucky to the Land of Ev to reverse his curse. As soon as they start their journey, they find out how Ojo the Unlucky earned his name, they are plagued with the worst bad luck they've ever seen!

5.title: Rules of Attraction/Brain Power of Love

episode of.title: Dorothy and the Wizard of Oz (TV Series 2017– )

5.plot: To celebrate Valentine's Day, Ozma gifts Dorothy with an enchanted love magnet that causes everyone to fall in love with whoever is holding it. Scarecrow loses his brain power any time he's around his new crush, Patchwork Girl.

6.title: Jinxed/Rise of the Nome King

episode of.title: Dorothy and the Wizard of Oz (TV Series 2017– )

6.plot: A jinx curse takes the voices of Dorothy and Ozma hours before Ozma needs to give a speech. When Scarecrow gets love-struck, Tin Man's mouth rusts shut, and Lion eats sticky peanut butter, Toto has to negotiate with a two-headed yak for the cure to the jinx curse. Dorothy finds the Magic Magnifying Glass of Oz that can change anything's size, but the Nome King steals it to grow himself big and take over Oz.

7.title: One-Winged Wally/Wand-erful

episode of.title: Dorothy and the Wizard of Oz (TV Series 2017– )

7.plot: The gang helps a runaway flying monkey with only one wing get a second wing from the Crooked Magician, but it's the one-winged way that saves the day. Only Glinda's bubbles will protect Emerald City from a nasty storm, but she can't find her wand. Unfortunately, Wilhelmina gets to it first.

8.title: No Sleep Sleepover/Lion Catches a Bug

episode of.title: Dorothy and the Wizard of Oz (TV Series 2017– )

8.plot: Wilhelmina tries to ruin Dorothy's sleepover party in the Emerald Palace with a giant pillow monster. In Oz, "catching a bug" isn't an expression- Lion catches a literal bug that makes him sick, but he needs to get better so he can defend the Emerald Forest against some flying monkeys.

9.title: Tik Tok and Tin Man/If I Only Had Some Brawn

episode of.title: Dorothy and the Wizard of Oz (TV Series 2017– )

9.plot: The gang finds Tik Tok, a clockwork man broken down on the side of the road, and set out to fix him, but the presence of another metal man makes Tin Man feel insecure. Scarecrow gets a potion to grow muscles so he can impress Patchwork Girl, but the potion cuts his brainpower right when the gang needs it to stop the Nome King's latest corny plot.

10.title: The Beast Royales/Time After Time

episode of.title: Dorothy and the Wizard of Oz (TV Series 2017– )

10.plot: Everyone's favorite band, the Beast Royales, comes to Oz, but Wilhelmina, their #1 fan, kidnaps them so that only she can enjoy their music. Wilhelmina uses a time travel hourglass to make several attempts at stealing the ruby slippers while everyone in Oz is asleep.

11.title: Kitten Around/Castle Sitters

episode of.title: Dorothy and the Wizard of Oz (TV Series 2017– )

11.plot: Dorothy and the gang help a lost kitten and her family with a rak attacking the town of Purrville. / Glinda puts Dorothy and the gang in charge of watching her castle, especially a magic history book that can record and erase history.

12.title: Stuck on You/Family Matters

episode of.title: Dorothy and the Wizard of Oz (TV Series 2017– )

12.plot: It's Family Day in Oz, but Woozy doesn't have a family. Dorothy and friends set out to help Woozy find his family. But when their attempts to find Woozy's family go comically awry, Woozy bursts into tears. All his tears create a raging river that's sweeping through Oz! As Dorothy and friends save Woozy, they realize that they are a family.

13.title: The Emerald of Zog/Cooking Up Some Magic

episode of.title: Dorothy and the Wizard of Oz (TV Series 2017– )

13.plot:
Know what this is about?

14.title: Copy Cat/Snow Place Like Home

episode of.title: Dorothy and the Wizard of Oz (TV Series 2017– )

14.plot: Wilhelmina uses Queen Ozma's magic copy cat statue to make an army of Wilhelminas - a Wilhe-army. Ozma uses a magic snowglobe to bring snow to the Emerald City, but if it breaks, it'll snow forever in the place it broke, and Wilhelmina gets her hands on it.

15.title: Mirror Madness/Everything Coming Up Poppies

episode of.title: Dorothy and the Wizard of Oz (TV Series 2017– )

15.plot: Wilhemina steals Ozma's magic mirror but becomes so infatuated with herself that her reflection comes to life, and she has to do good deeds to bring it back down. Dorothy needs poppies for her Poppin' Poppies Parade float, but accidentally replicates the Wicked Witch's enchanted sleeping poppies and puts everyone to sleep.

16.title: A Cut Above the Rest/Abraca-Oops

episode of.title: Dorothy and the Wizard of Oz (TV Series 2017– )

16.plot: Ozma throws a royal ball in honor of Dorothy and tasks her with keeping the peace between Duchess Doofus and the Baroness Bunchausen. Dorothy learns that "Abracadabra" actually removes magic when she accidentally removes Ozma's magic right before a magic competition, so she and the gang secretly help Ozma cheat.

17.title: Halloween Heist/Haunt Me Not

episode of.title: Dorothy and the Wizard of Oz (TV Series 2017– )

17.plot: Dorothy teaches her friends about Halloween and everyone is very excited. The gang then decides to play a prank on Dorothy .

18.title: Wheelers Of Fortune/Sister Sister

episode of.title: Dorothy and the Wizard of Oz (TV Series 2017– )

18.plot: When chunks of the Yellow Brick Road go missing, Dorothy and friends follow a trail back to the Wheelers' camp, and find that Rustle stole the bricks to get out of racing with a broken wheel. Glinda's twin sister, Melinda the Mean, poses as Glinda and is mean to all the Munchkins to ruin Glinda's reputation and take power.

19.title: Moody Magic/If the Shoe Fits

episode of.title: Dorothy and the Wizard of Oz (TV Series 2017– )

19.plot:
Know what this is about?
 Be the first one to add a plot.

20.title: Get Smart/Mission Imp-Possible

episode of.title: Dorothy and the Wizard of Oz (TV Series 2017– )

20.plot: Nome King gets cranky about not being included in a book of Ozian rulers from the time he briefly took over, so he goes after the author, Professor Wagglebug. Wilhemina orders three mail-order imps and fires Frank and Lyman. Meanwhile, the Zoop gets the hiccups, causing earthquakes across Oz, because he thinks Ozma cursed him.

imdb.title: Dorothy and the Wizard of Oz
plot: _Dorothy and the Wizard of Oz_ (qv) is about Dorothy, who is granted princess of Emerald City by Queen Ozma after defeating the Wicked Witch.::CN
